Text: Nuggets Notes examples Cc Public Relations department is looking for a few quotes from traders see below examples to add to their next Ameriflash Newsletter If you would like to submit one you can email it to Michelle Vitrella The deadline to submit an entry for the next Ameriflash is Tomorrow at pm Anything turned in after the deadline will be added to the next issues of Ameriflash Thanks Rain Forwarded by Airam ArteagaHOUECT on AM From Michelle Vitrella PM Whats the message were trying to get across Ray Bowen COO EIM Im not a micromanager John Lavorato COO ENA Make it so number one Jeff Shankman COO EGM Im looking for some high velocity capital Brian Redmond PresidentHPL MD AssetsUpstream OriginationENA Can I get this NOW Gary Hickerson MD Equity TradingEGM Results not reasons Craig Breslau VPIndustrial Middle Market sENA Okay heres the deal Jean Mrha Beach VPUpstream OriginationENA Bigger faster Dave DelaineyCEOENA Four bid at five What do you want to do John Arnold Vice PresidentFinancialNymex Trading We trade weather Gary Taylor Manager Weather Risk Management Group You trade WHAT anyone Gary speaks with

Gas Fundamentals WebsiteForwarded by Airam ArteagaHOUECT on AM NRON AM Sent by Chris NRON To Airam CT Kimberly CT Ina CT Becky nron Jessica NRON Laura nron Amanda nron cc Subject Gas Fundamentals Website Please forward the following message to your groups We are proud to announce the launch of the production Gas Fundamentals websites at As you browse the website please feel free to use the contact button to send us any feedback and report any issues you might encounter If this is your first visit to the website there may be a few issues that you might encounter such as Your browser may prompt you to download a Macromedia Flash control Adobe PDF documents may prompt you to download them rather than opening in the browser If you encounter any of these issues please contact Demetrion Ware at Ext or Dave Dronet at Ext and we will work to resolve the issues as soon as possible NOTE This site will only function if you use Internet Explore or higher if you are trying to view the site using Netscape it will not function properly Thank you David Dronet

FW ICC gas NOI MeetingHello All Attached is a memo highlighting the issue areas covered by staff at the ICC meeting in Chicago yesterday If you have any questions feel free to call It was strange to hear Tom Kennedy say that staff supports reasonable hedging practices and forward contract purchases while sitting next to Zuraski who opposed recovery of same in the PGLC fixed price docket Incidentally Tom Kennedy noted several times that hedging will not necessarily reduce prices but will stabilize them

SPECIAL FILTERS FOR EAST DESK Cc from Tricia Spence Forwarded by Victor LamadridHOUECT on PM Russ Severson PM To Tricia CT Scott CT Victor CT Katherine L CT Edward CT Jayant CT Jeff CT George CT Scott CT Jeffrey C CT cc Subject SPECIAL FILTERS FOR EAST DESK PLEASE FIND ATTACHED NEW PIPE FILTERS For the full East desk intramonth position you can apply the portfolio for EAST INTRAMONTH POSITION no filters If you want to view the positions by NE and SE pipes save the following views on your machine To use the special filter portfolios after you launch position manager open the following views The system will activate the portfolio for the respective pipes and display only the requested pipes for the deals with NE and SE pipes MAKE SURE YOU DO NOT HAVE A POSITION MANAGER ACTIVE WHEN YOU DETACH THE NEW FILTERS ON YOUR PC DOUBLE CLICK ON THE FILE BELOW SELECT LAUNCH AND OK THEN LAUNCH POSITION MANAGER AND THE FILTERS WILL BE IN YOUR SAVED VIEWS

Alliance Pipeline Infobelow is from Hunter Shively Please Read Thanks Rain Forwarded by Hunter S ShivelyHOUECT on PM Richard NRON AM To Hunter S CT cc Subject Alliance Pipeline Info Alliance presented this to PGL when they were here on Tuesday its the firm shippers primary deliver pointsAs an interesting note PGL interconnect will allow but their system cant handle it Were working with our Canadian office to buy some of this alliance gas for PGL What we are looking at is reducing your baseload sale and part of their DIQ and replacing it with alliance gas Well talk about it later Forwarded by Richard TomaskiCorpEnron on AM Barbara G Dillard AM To Richard nron Cary M nron Steve NRON Russell E nron Roy NRON Kevin P nron cc Laura nron Subject Alliance Pipeline Info FYI Forwarded by Barbara G DillardCorpEnron on AM on AM To Barbara G CT cc Subject Alliance Pipeline Info Barbara I met with some people from Alliance Pipeline yesterday to discuss nominations and confirmations Attached is a piece of information that might be of interest to the daily group Could you route to the rest of the group Thanks Alliance Shipper Delivery Capacities Alliance Shipper Delivery Capacitiesdoc

FW VegasOriginal Message From Dee Espinoza ENRON mailtoIMCEANOTESDeeEspinozaCdeeEespinozatravelparkEcomE NRONcom Sent Friday June PM To Arteaga Airam Subject Vegas I can get the Bellagio on a package for using Funjet Dep IAH p Arr LAS pm on CO Dep LAS p Arr IAH pm on CO The package includes rt air rt transfers nights at Bellagio in a lakeview room pretrip cancellation waiver for for The Venetian is not available on any package We can do the air on CO for each and the hotel has categories of suites available The hotel is all suites The rate changes every night for this period Standard Luxury Suite Fri Sat Sun sq ft sunken living room king bed Vista Luxury Suite Fri Sat SUn same suite but with a guaranteed view The view is of the Treasure Islands erupting volcano on one side or the pirate ship show on the other side NO PRICE IS GUARANTEED UNTIL PAID FOR AND TICKETED There were only seats available on CO at this price on the return flight if booked separately and not in package deal Dee Espinoza Travel Agency in the Park Lamar ste Houston Tx direct line fax
